{"arkId":"cl010446164","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010446164","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Coffret \u00e0 bijoux de la Duchesse de Berry","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret \u00e0 bijoux de la Duchesse de Berry"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Charles X (1824-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine-\u003ERestauration (1814-1830)-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1829","currentLocation":"Louvre-Lens","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1829,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"1er tiers du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"},{"label":"Leloy, Jean-Charles-Fran\u00e7ois","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"23\/07\/1774","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1846","place":"Boulogne","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2019.16.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"coffret","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Coffret en forme de ch\u00e2sse gothique avec frise d\u0027arcatures \u00e0 la base, encadrement du portrait de Marie-Caroline de Bourbon-Sicile, duchesse de Berry en ogive avec trilobes dans les \u00e9coin\u00e7ons, rosaces au dos, pinacles et clochetons en bronze ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s par Louis Honor\u00e9 Bocquet.\r\nLe portrait est peint par Germaine Aim\u00e9e Perlet d\u0027apr\u00e8s la miniature de Guglielmo Faija, inspir\u00e9e elle-m\u00eame du grand portrait de Dubois-Drahonnet.\r\nLes m\u00e9daillons des autres plaques du coffret, peints par Boudet, m\u00ealent des bijoux et des ustensiles garnissant g\u00e9n\u00e9ralement les n\u00e9cessaires, sugg\u00e9rant un double usage : coffret \u00e0 bijoux et bo\u00eete \u00e0 ouvrage.\r\n\r\nLe coffret de style gothique, en porcelaine dure et bronze dor\u00e9, est command\u00e9 en 1829 \u00e0 la manufacture de S\u00e8vres par la duchesse de Berry, qui encourageait la mode du n\u00e9o-gothique. Il est cr\u00e9\u00e9 sur des dessins de l\u0027ornemaniste Charles-Fran\u00e7ois Leloy.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"28,3","displayDimension":"28,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"34","displayDimension":"34 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"23,5","displayDimension":"23,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : bronze (dor\u00e9)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : porcelaine dure","placeOfCreation":"S\u00e8vres (Ile-de-France = Ile de France-\u003EHauts-de-Seine = Hauts de Seine)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Don manuel consenti en m\u00e9moire du Comte Brando Brandolini d\u2019Adda par l\u2019interm\u00e9diaire de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Comtesse Brandolini d\u0027Adda, Cristiana","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre","note":"","role":", Interm\u00e9diaire"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de commission des acquisitions","value":"17\/04\/